msgid ""
"A ScrollContainer node with a :ref:`Control<class_control>` child and "
"scrollbar child (HScrollbar, :ref:`VScrollBar<class_vscrollbar>`, or "
"both) will only draw the Control within the ScrollContainer area.  "
"Scrollbars will automatically be drawn at the right (for vertical) or "
"bottom (for horizontal) and will enable dragging to move the viewable "
"Control (and its children) within the ScrollContainer.  Scrollbars will "
"also automatically resize the grabber based on the minimum_size of the "
"Control relative to the ScrollContainer.  Works great with a "
":ref:`Panel<class_panel>` control.  You can set EXPAND on children size "
"flags, so they will upscale to ScrollContainer size if ScrollContainer "
"size is bigger (scroll is invisible for chosen dimension)."
